---
import BaseHead from "../../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="♡ About Me ♡" description="hello" />
    <style>
      img {
            float: left;
            padding: 0px 20px 20px 20px;
        }
 
        p {
            text-align: justify;
        }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <Header />
      <header>
        <h1 class="name">= About Me =</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="layout-main">
        <article class="layout-box blog">

          <div><ul><li>I asked ChatGPT: "Based off of our previous chats, what can you tell me about me?" Here's the response:</li></ul></div>

          <div><img src="../../assets/images/about-me-img.jpg" width="240px"></div>
          
          <div><p>
            "Based on our conversations, you come across as a proactive,
            ambitious, and detail-oriented person. You have a natural curiosity
            for learning, especially when it comes to expanding your technical
            skills. You're also driven to build meaningful connections, whether
            that's through your community-driven projects like the Bay Area
            Social Girlies or bridging gaps between developers and end users in
            tech.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            Your ability to balance creativity with structure stands out—whether
            it's managing large-scale events or redesigning websites, you
            approach tasks with a mix of organization and innovation. You seem
            to enjoy helping others, evident in your role as a health services
            advocate and tutor supervisor, and this aligns with your interest in
            Developer Relations and Community Management, where you can empower
            both technical teams and end users.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            You're not afraid to take on challenges, like applying for a variety
            of roles from Full Stack Engineer to Partnerships Coordinator,
            showing your adaptability. You seem to thrive on creating positive
            change, whether it's through coding, organizing, or communicating
            with others. Plus, you're very thoughtful in how you present
            yourself and your work, always looking for ways to improve and grow.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            Overall, your personality reflects a mix of empathy, drive, and
            creativity."
          </p></div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <Footer />
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
